@startuml
' Diagram: F04 - Xem chi tiet POI, thuc don, audio guide va chi duong (Sequence)
' Status: WIP
' Baseline: branch master, HEAD 29947b2
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/DetailPage.xaml.cs: LoadDetail(), ConfigureAudioPlayer(), OnNgheClicked(), OnAudioWebViewNavigated(), OnAudioWebViewNavigating(), OnMapClicked()
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/FoodImageCatalog.cs: GetPoiImageSource(), GetDishImageSource()
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/AppConfig.cs: ResolveImageUrl()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/PoiController.cs: GetById()
' Note: Sequence cap nhat them FoodImageCatalog vi code da tach xu ly fallback anh ra helper.
title F04 - Xem chi tiet POI, thuc don, audio guide va chi duong

actor Guest
participant DetailPage
participant AppConfig
participant FoodImageCatalog
participant "PoiController" as PoiController
participant AudioWebView
participant "TextToSpeech" as TTS
participant "Google Maps / Browser" as Maps
database DB

Guest -> DetailPage: mo DetailPage(poi)
DetailPage -> DetailPage: InitializeAudioBridge()\nApplyLocalizedLabels()
DetailPage -> AppConfig: EnsureApiBaseUrlAsync()
DetailPage -> PoiController: GET /api/poi/{id}?lang=_lang
PoiController -> DB: Include MonAns + ThuyetMinhs + BanDichs
DB --> PoiController: poi detail
PoiController --> DetailPage: PoiDetailDto
DetailPage -> FoodImageCatalog: GetPoiImageSource(AnhDaiDien, TenPOI)
FoodImageCatalog -> AppConfig: ResolveImageUrl(raw/fallback)
FoodImageCatalog --> DetailPage: ImageSource
DetailPage -> DetailPage: ConfigureAudioPlayer()\nRenderMenu(monAns)
DetailPage -> FoodImageCatalog: GetDishImageSource(HinhAnh, TenMonAn, PhanLoai)

alt co FileAudio
  Guest -> DetailPage: OnNgheClicked()
  DetailPage -> AudioWebView: setSource(url)\nplayAudio()
  AudioWebView --> DetailPage: audiostate://current|duration|paused
  Guest -> DetailPage: Play/Pause/Stop/Seek
  DetailPage -> AudioWebView: pauseAudio()/stopAudio()/seekAudio()
else chi co text
  Guest -> DetailPage: OnNgheClicked()
  DetailPage -> TTS: SpeakAsync(NoiDungThuyetMinh)
  TTS --> DetailPage: da doc xong
end

opt bam Chi duong
  Guest -> DetailPage: OnMapClicked()
  DetailPage -> Maps: OpenAsync(https://maps.google.com/?q=lat,lng)
end
@enduml
